description: Try our easy to follow Tacos with Southern Style Crumbed Fish Bites & Mexican Bean Salad recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Tacos with Southern Style Crumbed Fish Bites & Mexican Bean Salad Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 410g can red kidney beans, rinsed, drained

recipeInstructions.text: Mix together 410g can of rinsed and drained red kidney beans, 1 diced Lebanese cucumber, 8 quartered Sweet Solanato Tomatoes and 1 peeled and diced avocado in a bowl. Add juice of 1/2 lime and toss gently.
Cook Southern Style Crumbed Fish Bites and chunky chips according to the packet instructions. Serve fish bites divided in Mexican taco shells with bean salad, sour cream, lime wedges and chips.
